::Battera::
She fell back from the slap.  She had finally had enough of these 
bot.  She transformed into bat mode and fired her optic lazars at 
Vulois. "Creep!" She flew past him and down the hall.  She opened her 
link to CyberShark. "I'm out of here. I'm tired of being pushed 
around and treated like a maximal around here. Call me when your 
ready to meet up."  She flew out around the corner and out the 
entrance, past Zardus and Feline and HotRod and the others.  As she 
past Zardus,"Thanks for everything." She flew up high into the sky 
and up into the clouds.  Her face still stung from the slap and she 
had a red hand print on her cheek.
